def generate_cyclic_permutations(N: int) -> list[int]:
    l = [N]
    i = 2
    ln = len(str(N))
    mul = 10 ** (ln - 1)
    while i < ln:
        v = l[len(l) - 1]
        rem = v % 10
        qu = v // 10
        ans = mul * rem + qu
        if ans in l:
            break
        else:
            l.append(ans)
            i += 1
    return l
